{"id": "hard_combo_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Combinatorics", "question": "证明：正整数n拆分为互不相同正整数之和的方法数，等于拆分为奇数之和的方法数。（用生成函数）", "answer": "互不相同分割GF:∏(1+q^k)。奇数分割GF:∏1/(1-q^{2k-1})。由(1+q^k)=(1-q^{2k})/(1-q^k)得一式=∏1/(1-q^{2k-1})。"}
{"id": "hard_nt_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Number Theory", "question": "求所有正整数解 (x,y) 满足 x² - y² = 2024。", "answer": "x²-y²=(x-y)(x+y)=2024=2³×11×23。解得：(x,y)=(507,505),(255,251),(69,59),(57,43),(39,17),(33,5)"}
{"id": "hard_ineq_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Inequality", "question": "证明：对任意正实数x,y,z，有x/(y+z)+y/(z+x)+z/(x+y) ≥ 3/2。（Nesbitt不等式）", "answer": "令S=x+y+z，则原式=∑S/(S-x)-3。由柯西∑S/(S-x)≥9/(∑(S-x)/S)=9/2。故原式≥3/2。"}
{"id": "hard_combo_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Combinatorics", "question": "从1到100中随机选3个不同数，求构成等差数列的概率。", "answer": "总C(100,3)=161700。等差数列总数=2∑_{d=1}^{49}(100-2d)=4900。概率=4900/161700=49/1617≈3.03%"}
{"id": "hard_ode_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Differential Equations", "question": "求解 y''+4y=sin(2x), y(0)=0, y'(0)=1", "answer": "yh=C₁cos2x+C₂sin2x, yp=-(x/4)cos2x。y=(5/8)sin2x-(x/4)cos2x。"}
